Output completions-demo.gif
Set Shell bash
Set FontSize 16
Set Width 1000
Set Height 420
Set Padding 16
Set TypingSpeed 45ms
Hide
Type "export PATH=/home/ra/Projects/open-source/twc-rs/target/release:$PATH"
Enter
Type "source <(COMPLETE=bash twc-rs)"
Enter
Type "clear"
Enter
Show
Sleep 500ms
Type "twc-rs apps logs "
Sleep 600ms
Tab
Sleep 700ms
Tab
Sleep 2.5s
Type "ra"
Sleep 400ms
Tab
Sleep 700ms
Tab
Sleep 3s
